00:50:21,020 --> 00:50:28,180
♫ I won't lie, lie to you ♫

765
00:50:40,441 --> 00:50:43,435
[Summer Strike]

766
00:50:43,435 --> 00:50:45,991
Shall we meet in front of the library daily and go jogging?

767
00:50:45,991 --> 00:50:48,186
- Shall we go to a movie?
- And fried chicken and beer?

768
00:50:48,186 --> 00:50:49,833
Noona, that hurts.

769
00:50:49,833 --> 00:50:52,508
I feel like I'm getting hurt by you as well.

770
00:50:52,508 --> 00:50:55,656
Trauma isn't easily forgotten; the body is smarter than you think.
[I know you're the one who killed Seon Ah.]

771
00:50:55,656 --> 00:50:56,631
Dae Beom!

772
00:50:56,631 --> 00:50:59,741
He tried his best to endure with all his strength.

773
00:50:59,741 --> 00:51:01,721
But that all collapsed today.

774
00:51:01,721 --> 00:51:04,481
Can you take responsibility for Dae Beom's life?

775
00:51:04,481 --> 00:51:06,141
I can do it.

776
00:51:06,141 --> 00:51:09,653
For you, it might be just a summer fling in a beach town,

777
00:51:09,653 --> 00:51:12,383
but my relationship with Dae Beom is different.
